OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FA US delegation led by Vice President
OL,7,FJD Vance arrived in Pakistan for talks
OL,8,Fwith Iranian officials on Saturday.
OL,10,FThe talks are aimed at cementing a
OL,11,F'fragile' ceasefire, paving the way
OL,12,Ffor a permanent end to the fighting.
OL,14,FIt marks the first such meeting since
OL,15,Fthe war began more than a month ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
