FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FThe ceasefire brokered by Pakistan
OL,7,Fstill faces hurdles in the talks
OL,8,Fbeginning on Saturday, as Israel and
OL,9,FHezbollah militants have been trading
OL,10,Ffire along the border of southern
OL,11,FLebanon, and Iran has set conditions
OL,12,Fbefore negotiations can begin.
OL,14,FVance arrived in Islamabad at the head
OL,15,Fof a delegation that includes
OL,16,FPresident Donald Trump's special envoy
OL,17,FSteve Witkoff and his son-in-law Jared
OL,18,FKushner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FThe Iranian delegation, led by
OL,7,FParliament Speaker Mohammad Bagher
OL,8,FQalibaf, was already in Islamabad.
OL,10,FBefore departing for Pakistan, Vance
OL,11,Fwarned Iran not to "play" the US.
OL,13,FHours later, Qalibaf said discussions
OL,14,Fwould only take place if there is an
OL,15,FIsraeli ceasefire in Lebanon and the
OL,16,Frelease of blocked Iranian assets.
OL,18,FHours earlier, President Donald Trump
OL,19,Fwished Vance good luck. "We'll find
OL,20,Fout what's going on. They're
OL,21,Fmilitarily defeated."
OL,26,@sD@TOUsD@YO]{D@YOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FHe echoed comments he made on his
OL,7,FTruth Social platform earlier in the
OL,8,Fday, where he said Iran had "no cards"
OL,9,Fin the peace talks, and "the only
OL,10,Freason they are alive today is to
OL,11,Fnegotiate".
OL,13,FThe Iranian delegation is scheduled to
OL,14,Fmeet with Pakistani Prime Minister
OL,15,FShehbaz Sharif at noon Saturday,
OL,16,Faccording to the Tasnim news agency,
OL,17,Fwhich is close to the powerful
OL,18,FRevolutionary Guard.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FThe talks come as the Lebanese
OL,7,FNational News Agency reported multiple
OL,8,FIsraeli strikes early Saturday in
OL,9,Fsouthern Lebanon, killing at least
OL,10,Fthree people.
OL,12,FThe three were killed when an
OL,13,Fairstrike hit and destroyed a
OL,14,Fresidential building in Maifadoun town
OL,15,Fin the southern province of Nabatiyeh,
OL,16,Faccording to the agency.
OL,18,FHezbollah, meanwhile, said it fired a
OL,19,Fbarrage of rockets that targeted a
OL,20,Fmilitary facility in northern Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FThe strikes increase the pressure on
OL,7,Fthe peace talks. Iran's parliamentary
OL,8,Fspeaker claimed that negotiations
OL,9,Fcouldn't begin until the mutually
OL,10,Fagreed-upon ceasefire, which they say
OL,11,Fincludes Lebanon, commences.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
