PN,30207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FIran has repeatedly said the ceasefire
OL,7,Fcovers attacks against its Lebanon-
OL,8,Fbased proxy Hezbollah, but Israel has
OL,9,Fsaid the ceasefire does not include
OL,10,FLebanon.
OL,12,FSources familiar with the last-minute
OL,13,Fceasefire negotiations on Tuesday told
OL,14,FITV News that the United States
OL,15,Fbelieved the agreement did extend to
OL,16,FLebanon.
OL,18,FTheir account appears to contradict
OL,19,Fclaims by the White House on Wednesday
OL,20,Fthat "Lebanon is not part of the
OL,21,Fceasefire".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
