FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FOn Friday evening, Lebanese officials
OL,7,Fsaid direct talks with Israel would
OL,8,Fstart on Tuesday to negotiate a
OL,9,Fceasefire. These will be held in
OL,10,FWashington, with the US acting as
OL,11,Fmediators.
OL,13,FHezbollah did not immediately comment
OL,14,Fon the development, though it has
OL,15,Fopposed direct talks with Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
