PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FDuring the past 40 days of war, more
OL,7,Fthan 1,900 people in Lebanon have been
OL,8,Fkilled in Israeli strikes, and more
OL,9,Fthan one million others have been
OL,10,Fdisplaced, according to government
OL,11,Ffigures.
OL,13,FMuch of the talks will focus on how to
OL,14,Fkeep the vital shipping route through
OL,15,Fthe Strait of Hormuz open.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
