FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FStarmer told ITV News' Talking
OL,7,FPolitics on Thursday that there needs
OL,8,Fto be "toll-free navigation" as part
OL,9,Fof the ceasefire, amid reports that
OL,10,FIran wants to charge $1 per oil barrel
OL,11,Fpassing through.
OL,13,FIran's deputy foreign minister said on
OL,14,FThursday that "the Strait of Hormuz is
OL,15,Fopen", but that any vessel wishing to
OL,16,Fpass through would need guidance from
OL,17,FIranian authorities to do so.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,F"Anybody who communicates with the
OL,7,FIranian authority has got permission
OL,8,Fto pass," Dr Saeed Khatibzadeh told
OL,9,FITV News International Editor Emma
OL,10,FMurphy.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, Starmer said Israel is
OL,13,F"wrong" to continue its strikes on
OL,14,FLebanon during the ceasefire, saying
OL,15,Fit "should stop" as a "matter of
OL,16,Fprinciple".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775923883
OL,3,CVance arrives in Pakistan for talks
OL,4,Cwith Iran over 'fragile' ceasefire
OL,6,FWhen asked whether the strikes were a
OL,7,Fbreach of the ceasefire, the prime
OL,8,Fminister said: "It's hard to say that
OL,9,Fthere is a breach when we haven't all
OL,10,Fgot access to all the details of the
OL,11,Fceasefire.
OL,13,F"But let me be really clear about it.
OL,14,FThey're wrong. That shouldn't be
OL,15,Fhappening. That should stop."
OL,17,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,18,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,19,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,20,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
